extendedInfo.description: You may not like fishing but fish frizzle game will turn you an absolutefisherman for an elongated period. It is a fun game developed by ObjectSol Technologies built with all splendorous experience of fish hunting andbarbecue. The game will engross you by its funny rhythm and fairy earmarks.Once started the game you will land in a boat sailing in a lagoon armed withFishing wheel and hook.You need to catch fishes to earn funds and get promoted to next higher level. There are scopes for making fry with fishes you have collected but you should be alert to protect them from birds approaching them. Frying a fish require an oven that you can buy with your funds you have earned. There are plenty of obstacles in different levels of game which you need to qualify and win within a stipulated time period.
